      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1778078365947,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "Summarize Relevant\nFacts",
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "jPMtNwW5By9ekpzBXILxO",
      "originalText": "Summarize Relevant\nFacts"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "version": 2870,
      "versionNonce": 1183385184,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "id": "AE3E5VGoEuWvmZGLzc_SS",
      "fillStyle": "hachure",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "x": 986.3589331796394,
      "y": -233.1806387946707,
      "strokeColor": "#000000",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "width": 967.718994140625,
      "height": 792,
      "seed": 1559389932,
      "groupIds": [],
      "roundness": null,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1778078365947,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "1. User enters N-th question in the conversation\n\n2. Memory Save: question copied to background thread to not block \nimmediate processing\n\n3. Memory Save background:\n- Detect facts included in the question (using LLM call)\n- Retrieve similar facts saved in memory (using Vector DB search)\n- Deduplicate then save new facts\n- Remove obsolete facts\n\n4. Memory Retrieve:\n- Get relevant facts from user memory (using Vector DB search)\n\n5. Based on Chat State, select agent (Orchestrate, Learn, Prepare or Reflect)\n\n5. Build Agent prompt:\n- Include System Prompt for selected Agent\n- Include tools definitions\n- Include past N steps of conversation chain\n- Include new question\n- Include retrieved Memory Facts at the end (to not bust the LLM cache)\n\n6. Call LLM\n\n8. If the LLM responds saying \"you need to call a set of tools:\n- Agent calls the tools in parallel\n- Agent includes the tools output as a user turn, and calls LLM again\n\n9. If the LLM just responds with chat answer:, the answer is streamed back to the Frontan\n\nNote:\nThe Agent saves all steps of the conversation in the local DB, to maintain conversation history.",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1. User enters N-th question in the conversation\n\n2. Memory Save: question copied to background thread to not block \nimmediate processing\n\n3. Memory Save background:\n- Detect facts included in the question (using LLM call)\n- Retrieve similar facts saved in memory (using Vector DB search)\n- Deduplicate then save new facts\n- Remove obsolete facts\n\n4. Memory Retrieve:\n- Get relevant facts from user memory (using Vector DB search)\n\n5. Based on Chat State, select agent (Orchestrate, Learn, Prepare or Reflect)\n\n5. Build Agent prompt:\n- Include System Prompt for selected Agent\n- Include tools definitions\n- Include past N steps of conversation chain\n- Include new question\n- Include retrieved Memory Facts at the end (to not bust the LLM cache)\n\n6. Call LLM\n\n8. If the LLM responds saying \"you need to call a set of tools:\n- Agent calls the tools in parallel\n- Agent includes the tools output as a user turn, and calls LLM again\n\n9. If the LLM just responds with chat answer:, the answer is streamed back to the Frontan\n\nNote:\nThe Agent saves all steps of the conversation in the local DB, to maintain conversation history."
    },
